.SH DIAGNOSTICS
The following error messages may be displayed:
.RS
.IP "Package name cannot be empty"
The package name field is required.
.IP "Package name too long (max 255 characters)"
Package names must be 255 characters or less.
.IP "Package name contains invalid characters"
Package names cannot contain special characters like !#$&*|;:"<>?/\\[]{}.
.IP "Package name must start with alphanumeric character"
Package names must start with a letter or number.
.IP "Package name cannot contain spaces"
Package names cannot have spaces.
.IP "Version must follow semantic versioning (e.g., 1.0.0)"
Versions must be in the format X.Y.Z.
.IP "Invalid email format"
Email addresses must be in a valid format.
.RE
